context:
KR:
&lt;color=#cc2424&gt;아니, 그렇게 우습다는 듯이 놀리지 말아라.&lt;/color&gt;
EN:
&lt;color=#cc2424&gt;Nay, tease me not, jest me not as though my venture is one for fools.&lt;/color&gt;

KR:
&lt;color=#cc2424&gt;그건 네가 모험이라는 것을 잘 몰라서 하는 소리라고 하지 않았느냐.&lt;/color&gt;
EN:
&lt;color=#cc2424&gt;I have already explained that you do not know of true adventure.&lt;/color&gt;

KR:
&lt;color=#cc2424&gt;우리는 지금부터 유례가 없는 치열한 고행을 치르러 갈 것이다.&lt;/color&gt;
EN:
&lt;color=#cc2424&gt;We shall soon walk a path of suffering, its intensity unprecedented and monumental.&lt;/color&gt;

KR:
&lt;color=#cc2424&gt;네 눈에는 보이지 않느냐, 위대한 모험의 문이 우리에게 활짝 열려 있다.&lt;/color&gt;
EN:
&lt;color=#cc2424&gt;Do you not see the grand gate of adventure risen, unlatched before us?&lt;/color&gt;

KR:
&lt;color=#cc2424&gt;그러니 잔말 말고 어서 채비를 갖추고 출발하자.&lt;/color&gt;
EN:
&lt;color=#cc2424&gt;Thus, silence your prattling and resume the preparations; let us leave posthaste.&lt;/color&gt;

KR:
&lt;color=#ffef23&gt;…….&lt;/color&gt;
EN:
&lt;color=#ffef23&gt;…….&lt;/color&gt;

KR:
&lt;color=#ffef23&gt;하지만 조금 이상하다는 생각은 드는군.&lt;/color&gt;
EN:
&lt;color=#ffef23&gt;... This is quite odd, however.&lt;/color&gt;

KR:
&lt;color=#ffef23&gt;……. &lt;/color&gt;
EN:
&lt;color=#ffef23&gt;……. &lt;/color&gt;

KR:
&lt;color=#ffef23&gt;로시난테가 언제부터 말을 할 수 있었단 말인가.&lt;/color&gt;
EN:
&lt;color=#ffef23&gt;Since when was Rocinante given the gift of speech?&lt;/color&gt;

KR:
&lt;누가 살아남은 건지도 모르니까 답답하긴 하네.&gt;
EN:
&lt;It is pretty suffocating to just sit here, not knowing who won the fight... or if there even was a fight.&gt;

KR:
&lt;…….&gt;
EN:
&lt;…….&gt;

KR:
&lt;오오, 뭔데?&gt;
EN:
&lt;Ooh, what is it?&gt;

KR:
&lt;color=#cc2424&gt;가족이나 형제는 없었던 거니?&lt;/color&gt;
EN:
&lt;color=#cc2424&gt;Where's your family? Your siblings?&lt;/color&gt;

KR:
&lt;color=#ffef23&gt;나는 날때부터 혼자였어. 언제나 추웠고 외로워서…&lt;/color&gt;
EN:
&lt;color=#ffef23&gt;I never had anyone, not even on the day I was born. I've only known... the cold... the loneliness...&lt;/color&gt;

KR:
&lt;color=#cc2424&gt;그렇다면 내가…&lt;/color&gt;
EN:
&lt;color=#cc2424&gt;Then let me…&lt;/color&gt;

KR:
&lt;color=#cc2424&gt;더 이상 죽고 싶지 않게 만들어주마. &lt;/color&gt;
EN:
&lt;color=#cc2424&gt;... grant you the will to live.&lt;/color&gt;

KR:
&lt;color=#cc2424&gt;너에게 영원히 함께 할 가족을 줄 테니, 나를 따라오렴.&lt;/color&gt;
EN:
&lt;color=#cc2424&gt;The family I shall grant you will forever be by your side. Come with me.&lt;/color&gt;
